news.title: Kamdhenu rallies 12% as NCLT approves demerger of paint business
news.para: Kamdhenu Colour and Coatings Limited will be listed separately as the second resulting company, the building material maker's regulatory filing added.

news.title: Saudi Arabia: Retal Urban Development prices IPO at top of range
news.para: The book-building process generated orders of 90.3 billion riyals, in a sign of strong momentum for Saudi Arabia's IPO market that has defied the global trend.

news.title: Thiruvananthapuram: 94 families to be affected by Varkala bypass project
news.para: The project will require acquisition of 2.04 hectares of land. The road will run through Chaluvila, Kollamkonam, Cherukunnam and Sivagiri wards in Varkala municipality.
